1
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,959
Wash your hands before eating.

2
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,439
You.

3
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,319
Uncle Houzi.

4
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,439
Did you take your medicine?

5
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:23,719
I'm pretty much recovered already.

6
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,480
See?

7
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,359
No.

8
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,000
You still need to take it for a few more months.

9
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:29,400
You know full well...

10
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,519
how awful that medicine tastes.

11
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:31,799
That's why...

12
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:33,200
you need to take it for a few more months.

13
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:34,840
I...

14
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,719
Did you take your medicine?

15
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:45,400
No.

16
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,000
Why not?

17
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:51,159
I feel I've been doing pretty well lately.

18
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:52,840
Go get your medicine.

19
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,200
The medicine's all gone.

20
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:01,959
Then go buy some.

21
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,400
Take her to buy some.

22
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:06,040
Let's go. Should be fine, right?

23
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,639
Are we out of medicine?

24
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,840
Looks like I need to hurry up...

25
00:02:21,639 --> 00:02:23,000
and brew more special medicine.

26
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,319
Lord Zishu.

27
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,560
The one who came...

28
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:32,719
He... he isn't Su Yang.

29
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:34,240
Useless.

30
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,879
Though the one who came isn't Su Yang,

31
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,479
among these two,

32
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,400
there's a child named Tongtong.

33
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:43,400
She's the person Su Yang treasures most.

34
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:45,599
If we capture her,

35
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,879
Su Yang will naturally come to us.

36
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,919
See?

37
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,520
This should last a while.

38
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,800
I'm fine now.

39
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,719
But you...

40
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,360
The doctor said you still can't eat...

41
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,840
anything too oily or salty.

42
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,599
Good thing we came to the hospital,

43
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:09,639
otherwise the wound could easily get infected.

44
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:12,599
Are we really not going to look around?

45
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,520
We hardly ever get out of Black Street.

46
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,360
Let's go to the bathhouse for a massage,

47
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:21,439
or hit a karaoke lounge and sing.

48
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,520
Uncle Houzi's gotta show you the world today.

49
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,560
Uncle Houzi's got money.

50
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,000
We'll head east first.

51
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,800
Head east, then...

52
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:34,120
First place on the left at East Second Alley.

53
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,680
Number seven is the prettiest.

54
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,159
Qiushui Bathhouse has three basement floors,

55
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,280
right under the garage.

56
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,000
You need a VIP referral to get in.

57
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,039
At Huangducheng Karaoke Lounge,

58
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:44,360
just fold a ten-yuan bill and hand it to the front desk,

59
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,319
and you can unlock the door to a new world.

60
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,280
How do you know all this?

61
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,840
Uncle Sangou told me.

62
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,439
He loves going to these places.

63
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:52,280
He rambles about it so much my ears are getting calluses.

64
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,759
When you're better, he can take you there.

65
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,879
But for now...

66
00:03:55,919 --> 00:03:56,800
we go home.

67
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,159
That Sangou...

68
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,080
really is a dog.

69
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:04,280
You know, some things...

70
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,639
you've gotta experience for yourself.

71
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,319
I said we're not going, so we're not.

72
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:08,479
If we head back this time,

73
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,039
there won't be another chance later.

74
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:10,680
Forget it.

75
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,680
Today's trip...

76
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:13,919
ends here.

77
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,639
Bosses.

78
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,240
You're just after money, right?

79
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,879
I know how things work on the streets.

80
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,040
I won't hide a single cent.

81
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:33,920
It's all here.

82
00:04:35,319 --> 00:04:36,120
Listen...

83
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,879
let's just be friends today.

84
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,920
The card's PIN is 686868.

85
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,720
It's not much.

86
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,959
Consider it drinks on me, bosses.

87
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:43,879
What do you say, boss?

88
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,519
Since you're being reasonable,

89
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,399
you can leave.

90
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,279
The kid stays.

91
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,879
Don't, boss.

92
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,439
How much money can a kid even make you?

93
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,399
And she has cancer.

94
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,199
How about this?

95
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,160
I'll make a call...

96
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,120
and have more money sent over.

97
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,040
Okay, boss?

98
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,600
Boss.

99
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,800
Don't test my patience.

100
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,560
I'll give you three seconds.

101
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,480
If you don't leave,

102
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,560
then stay forever.

103
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,199
Three.

104
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:09,279
If I run away now,

105
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,680
I could still tip someone off.

106
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,920
Uncle Houzi.

107
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,319
Just go.

108
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,480
I'll be fine.

109
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,360
Nobody kills for no reason.

110
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,079
Two.

111
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,920
Go.

112
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,240
You...

113
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,279
One.

114
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,120
Already at one?!

115
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,480
Stay back, all of you!

116
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,240
Don't come any closer!

117
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,120
Uncle Houzi!

118
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:15,959
Good thing my speed and strength have improved lately.

119
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:39,800
Uncle Houzi!

120
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,040
You can't fight anymore!

121
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,439
Your wounds are splitting open!

122
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,720
I'll go with them.

123
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,639
Gentlemen.

124
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,240
I'm just a rat in the gutter.

125
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:58,759
I'm not worthy of opposing you.

126
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,959
Why don't we just drop this?

127
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,680
Let's...

128
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,600
let bygones be bygones.

129
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:05,920
After all...

130
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,399
if one of you slipped up...

131
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:09,160
and traded your life for trash like me,

132
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,680
it really wouldn't be worth it.

133
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,839
What's your name?

134
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,079
Shen... Shen Hou.

135
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:28,959
Shen Hou.

136
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,120
Shen Hou, the Monkey.

137
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,439
What an offensive name.

138
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:42,519
Uncle Houzi!

139
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,160
Tongtong!

140
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,600
Run, now!

141
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,959
I'll only have a chance to live if you run!

142
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,680
Run!

143
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,680
Don't you dare!

144
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,839
Uncle Houzi!

145
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:04,199
I find that mortals these days

146
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,480
are generally far too arrogant.

147
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:09,959
Move.

148
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,240
Let me go!

149
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,920
Let me go!

150
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,279
Let her go!

151
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,360
Uncle Houzi!

152
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,079
Foolish.

153
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,639
You think you can bargain with this immortal?

154
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,959
Let me go!

155
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,959
Uncle Houzi!

156
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:30,000
Uncle Houzi!

157
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:36,960
Although...

158
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:40,320
I don't know how Shen Hou,

159
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:44,639
the Monkey, is offensive at all.

160
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,519
But I do know this:

161
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,480
when my father gave me this name,

162
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,720
it was...

163
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,840
because he hoped I would...

164
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,159
become a Divine Monkey!

165
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,639
Alone, I can stride into the heavens,

166
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,399
and laugh at the petty fiends filling the sky.

167
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,279
My name is Qi Tian.

168
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,440
I am Qi Tian!

169
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,360
Qi Tian.

170
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:14,159
My staff dances across the heavens.

171
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,039
What a pity.

172
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,879
You only have brute strength.

173
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,120
Uncle Houzi!

174
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,919
Uncle Houzi!

175
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,240
Uncle Houzi!

176
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:50,360
Behave yourself!

177
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,879
Let me go!

178
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:56,399
Uncle Houzi!

179
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:58,039
Just a Remnant Soul.

180
00:10:58,279 --> 00:10:59,559
Even after a thousand years,

181
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:01,080
it's still this powerful.

182
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,360
Lord Zishu.

183
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,399
Lord Zishu.

184
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:07,799
We should retreat for now.

185
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,200
Such a big disturbance

186
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,720
will surely draw Shanhai City's people.

187
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,399
With our current strength,

188
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:14,399
we can't face them head-on yet.

189
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:18,000
Are you saying

190
00:11:18,639 --> 00:11:20,360
this immortal can't beat those mortals?

191
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:20,840
No!

192
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,320
That's not what I meant at all.

193
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:24,159
Our target is Su Yang.

194
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,320
Until then,

195
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,320
we shouldn't risk any mishaps.

196
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,080
Besides, we've already captured Tongtong.

197
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,960
Now,

198
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:32,240
we just wait for Su Yang to walk right into his death.

199
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:34,039
Bunch of useless fools.

200
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,600
This high immortal isn't

201
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,000
as powerful as we imagined.

202
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:47,480
Tongtong.

203
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:51,919
Tongtong.

204
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,240
Go get Madman.

205
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,480
I can't die yet.

206
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,360
I'm begging you.

207
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,919
Take me to Black Street.

208
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,440
Please, I'm begging you.

209
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,799
Take me to Black Street.

210
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,320
Yellow Springs Clinic.

211
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,080
I'll take you.

212
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:26,240
Come on.

213
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,399
Come on.

214
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,000
Thank you.

215
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,200
The quality's pretty good.

216
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,120
Good stuff.

217
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,360
Isn't this guy one of Madman's people?

218
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:43,440
Didn't he go out with Tongtong this morning?

219
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:44,879
Where's Tongtong?

220
00:12:45,879 --> 00:12:46,960
Su Yang isn't at the clinic.

221
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,240
We've got big trouble now.

222
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:02,720
Can you help me to that spot?

223
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,360
Sure.

224
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,879
That's my spot.

225
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:08,840
Take it slow.

226
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,559
How are you holding up?

227
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:13,759
Thank you.

228
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,799
I should've given you some money.

229
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:18,559
No need.

230
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,519
No need.

231
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:31,879
In the end,

232
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,360
I still couldn't escape.

233
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,879
In that situation,

234
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,960
as a grown man,

235
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,600
who could bear

236
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:00,799
to abandon a child?

237
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:10,799
Why play the hero?

238
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:32,200
Tongtong.

239
00:14:34,399 --> 00:14:36,200
Captured.

240
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,559
In danger.

241
00:15:05,039 --> 00:15:06,399
You should get more sunlight.

242
00:15:06,399 --> 00:15:07,559
It'll heal your wounds faster.

243
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,120
No need.

244
00:15:09,279 --> 00:15:10,200
I'll just sit here.

245
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:15,080
Sunlight is good for you.

246
00:15:18,279 --> 00:15:19,879
I want some sun.

247
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:23,039
I really...

248
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,399
don't want to die.

249
00:15:34,399 --> 00:15:35,000
I'm...

250
00:15:37,399 --> 00:15:39,840
so afraid of dying.

251
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,080
The storyteller

252
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:24,799
roams everywhere.

253
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:27,120
Blood in every corner.

254
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:29,399
Madness in every corner.

255
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,159
I said

256
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:33,120
I'd never leave Black Street again.

257
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,879
I'm just a thief.

258
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,960
Why force me to fight?
